      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.5 - 老子 30.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>荊棘生焉。大軍之後，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the sequence of great armies there are sure to be bad years.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>必有凶年。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>A skilful (commander) strikes a decisive blow, and stops.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.8 - 老子 30.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.6 - 老子 30.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>善有果而已，不敢以取強。果而勿矜，果而勿伐，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He does not dare (by continuing his operations) to assert and complete his mastery. He will strike the blow, but will be on his guard against being vain or boastful or arrogant in consequence of it.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>果而勿驕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He strikes it as a matter of necessity;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-008">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>果而不得已，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>he strikes it, but not from a wish for mastery.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-009">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 30.14</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 30.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>果而勿強。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When things have attained their strong maturity they become old.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-030__align-010">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-030</prop>
